<font color="#FF0000">ON ROC'S</font><br>
<tt>Tue Sep 16 23:26:14 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
SW,<br><br>
The ROC were the most effective fighters I, too, have ever seen. We had a compound on one of our base camps. No mercy, no quarter, no Winter Soldiers, no nothing. Their sole objective was no gooks. They knew that Charlie only respected raw, brutal, inhuman, body part ripping, disembowling, frightfull and determined force, and the ROC's dished it out in spades. That is why Charlie never voluntarily attacked the ROC's. If they did, the entire area was systematically and effectively eliminated, hooch by hooch.<br><br>
Funny, I don't see the ROC's treated with contemptuous disdain in their country. I wonder why. Food for thought?
